      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/spain-s-economy-extends-post-covid-streak-with-0-8-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙经济是欧元区最大成员国中表现最好的国家，去年年底强劲增长，延续了 2020 年疫情封锁结束后开始的增长势头。]]></description>
